01:04:45.539 --> 01:04:50.589
of somebody whose perception of their skill
at deceiving was far off from their actual

01:04:50.589 --> 01:04:51.589
skill and they--

01:04:51.589 --> 01:04:52.839
&gt;&gt;Chris Chabris: Or for his skill at crime,
yeah.

01:04:52.839 --> 01:04:56.089
&gt;&gt;audience #10: Yeah. But isn't it possible,
I guess the way I interpret it when I saw

01:04:56.089 --> 01:05:02.000
