01:05:02.000 --> 01:05:06.130
of confidence that it was valid and that he
should be receiving money back.

01:05:06.130 --> 01:05:09.710
&gt;&gt;Chris Chabris: Well, that's certainly possible
and sometimes when I get angry at a customer

01:05:09.710 --> 01:05:11.110
service person, it helps a little bit.

01:05:11.110 --> 01:05:12.450
&gt;&gt;audience #10: Right.

01:05:12.450 --> 01:05:17.220
&gt;&gt;Chris Chabris: Yeah, that's a possible explanation
and I like that you called it the million-dollar

01:05:17.220 --> 01:05:21.780
bill experiment cause we didn't actually do
