01:06:10.490 --> 01:06:13.630
&gt;&gt;audience #11: You mentioned the distinction
between what we know in the head and what

01:06:13.630 --> 01:06:14.809
we can infer from the environment.

01:06:14.809 --> 01:06:15.809
&gt;&gt;Chris Chabris: Right.

01:06:15.809 --> 01:06:18.960
&gt;&gt;audience #11: And these days, more and more
