01:08:15.480 --> 01:08:20.880
you guys ever gone into biology, neurobiology
to see what parts of the brain's actually,

01:08:20.880 --> 01:08:23.560
are stimulated in the people that do see them?
And how does that differ?

01:08:23.560 --> 01:08:26.950
&gt;&gt;Chris Chabris: Well, the answer, the answer
